#DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The body of 13-year-old Enoch Mpianzi has been found in North West. He had gone missing during a water activity as part of a school camp hosted by Parktown Boys' High. The body was found by police. Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi says, "The family of Enoch Mpianza was fully briefed and we are all devastated by this tragic accident. Our thoughts are with the family and the school community."